ed support for \"echConfigList\" and \"echForceQuery\".\n- Minor Improvements & Fixes\nVarious small improvements and non-critical bug fixes to enhance overall stability.","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"4.5.0","secondarySubtitle":"Wed Mar 11 2026 13:14:55 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Hysteria configuration parsing fix (when downloading subscription)\n- VMESS pinSHACert added to manualInput UI\n- Accessibility (VoiceOver) small improvements\n- UI/UX emprovements as usual","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"4.4.3","secondarySubtitle":"Sat Feb 28 2026 13:37:20 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Minimal UI/UX fixes and emproved stability","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"4.4.0","secondarySubtitle":"Tue Feb 24 2026 05:21:26 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- New xray core v 26.1.23\n- App now support Hysteria2 configurations\n- Added support for pinnedPeerCertSha256 (TLSSettings)\n- Check current connection fix (no limit mode)\n- app no longer uses empty chunk geo files\n- announce expire button appearance fix","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"4.2.5","secondarySubtitle":"Fri Feb 13 2026 06:25:05 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Numerous small improvements and refinements to make the app more stable and convenient\n- Fixed an issue where ping could occasionally fail to stop\n- Cleaned up the Announcements section; it now works correctly\n- Added subscription refresh via long press with a forced status check\n- Brought back the includeAllNetworks killSwitch toggle in DevSettings for greater control\n- Updated the visual representation of the subscription refresh process\n- Added the ability to refresh all subscriptions with a single swipe down","style":"detail","wantsCol